  <description>
   Trebuchet is a VR studio based in Montreal, QC. We launched Prison Boss VR last August, which was very well received critically (87% on Steam) and won for the Microsoft Dream.Build.Play. contest in the mixed reality category. By combining our expertise in game design and in virtual reality, we are focused on bringing innovative and unique experiences to VR players. We are now launching our upcoming game Jousting Time on Kickstarter, on April 2nd, 2018.

  </description>

  <!-- Choose between a single block: -->
  <history>
    Founded in May 2017, Trebuchet aims to create great interactive content for VR.

    In July 2017, Trebuchet won the "Best Game Experience" award for the game jam entry BLACKHOLE FRIDAY at Jam Nations Montréal.

    In August 2017, Trebuchet releases its first game, Prison Boss VR, with a good reception from the VR community.
	
	In April 2018, Trebuchet launches a Kickstarter Campaign for its new project, Jousting Time.
  </history>

